    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two realities are divided by centuries — yet bound by the same fate, in a world where time itself overlaps due to an ancient curse,<br>Step into the intertwined destinies of <strong>Annelise A1</strong> Chosen of the First Age, and <strong>Annelise A3</strong>, her distant self in the Third. Through the power of the <strong>Pyrite Talisman</strong>, they can see each other across time — two souls walking parallel realities, united by the same path but separated by centuries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The demo introduces the <strong>prologue chapter</strong> and the <strong>first parallel sequence</strong> between the two Annelises.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the dark woods of the 1st Age, to the cold mountains of the 3rd Age, players will witness the first echoes of the coming Plagues — and the moment their timelines begin to converge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
